// chriz-sod-remix component 180 - override script for the celebration guests
// (csrnobm/csrnobf/csrffgd). They exist only for the plot-50 evening; vanilla
// dresses the palace with its own wandering nobles from plot 52 (BD0102.baf:307).
IF
  !Global("BD_PLOT","GLOBAL",50)
THEN
  RESPONSE #100
    DestroySelf()
END
